9600

Related Media

9600 Installation Instructions
9600 Configuration and Parts Identification
Hutchens Spring Appendix
Huckbolt Removal
Hutch Logo Locations

The 9600 series suspension features a two-piece tapered torque arm bushing that offers superior durability and maximum serviceability. Like our 9700, the 9600 series is available in fabricated or cast steel. Single, tandem and multi-axle configurations in a wide variety of axle spacings are available with weight capacities up to 25,000 lbs/axle.
